Nigerian comic skit maker and activist, Debo Adedayo, popularly known as Mr Macaroni, has stated he will never stop using women in creating his comic skits. Recall that the comedian has been criticized for always sexualizing and using women in his comic skits, however, he disclosed via his official Twitter page that he will also not stop portraying real-life situations in his videos. He wrote, “To Whom It May Concern: Mr Macaroni won’t stop using women in his contents. Thank you for your understanding. You are doing well. -Advertisement- “Also, Mr Macaroni will not stop portraying real-life situations in his contents. All of Mr Macaroni’s contents are also open to constructive criticisms. “We won’t always agree on everything. But we can always do better. Gracias.”